<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99908098312690></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99908098312690><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=99908098312690>Erudite Wiz Solo Tactics...</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=99908098312690#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=62442><span id= >LordAdam</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Aug 29th 6:29 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a 16 wizzy whom my Main has twinked out. She's erudite with some fairly decent gear. I have mainly concentrated on her INT and AGI with some extra mana items tossed in there. <br>I have solo'd her all the way from level 1 (with a few exceptions of course) As an erud I gained her levels around the west. starting with Qeynos, Qeynos hills. blackburrow for a short time just to get to level 12. and then, you hit 12 BLAM! your spells actually do good damage. I took her to North karana and solo'd on everything high blue to low red. Since druids love NK its releltively easy to get a SoW and if not just have a few potions handy. I have achieved 12 to 16 in a very short time. Once you get to know the safe spots in the zone and where to kite around at you're set from level 12 to 18.<br>     If you are making an erudite wizzy and are planning on twinking that wizzy a bit on the INT and AGI. try this tactic. the levels will fly by from 11-16 I garuntee. just be careful of NK, be wise and good luck! <br>16 Wizzy - Scorcea<br>Povar<br>AKA 39 Pally - Moralis<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
